      "author": "github-actions[bot]",
      "description": "## What’s changed\n\n- Removed `Document.createDocumentFragment` calls flagged by the Obsidian community-plugin audit.\n- Creates planner table cells through a typed Obsidian element instance helper and immediately detaches them before rendering.\n- Validates CSS colors with a typed Obsidian `createDiv` helper and removes the temporary element immediately.\n- Keeps the source free of direct `createElement`, `createElementNS`, `createDocumentFragment`, and unqualified global `createEl` calls.\n\n**Full changelog**: https://github.com/POBSIZ/obsidian-diary/compare/1.8.2...1.8.3",
