      "description": "## What’s changed\n\n- Replaced unqualified global `createEl` calls with typed `DocumentFragment.createEl` Obsidian helper calls.\n- Preserved detached table-cell and CSS-color validation behavior without inserting temporary nodes into the document.\n- Eliminated the resulting `no-unsafe-assignment`, `no-unsafe-call`, `no-unsafe-member-access`, `no-unsafe-return`, `no-unsafe-argument`, and `prefer-create-el` community-plugin audit warnings.\n\n**Full changelog**: https://github.com/POBSIZ/obsidian-diary/compare/1.8.1...1.8.2",
