      "author": "github-actions[bot]",
      "description": "## What’s changed\n\n- Unified planner chips, controls, modal actions, settings controls, and accessibility behavior across yearly, monthly grid, monthly list, daily, and 3-day views.\n- Preserved compact layout, scroll position, plan-note panels, recurrence state, calendar overlays, and planner interactions through shared UI and DOM primitives.\n- Refreshed desktop and narrow-layout screenshots, including new daily and 3-day timeline images.\n- Synchronized English, German, Spanish, French, Japanese, Korean, Simplified Chinese, and Traditional Chinese documentation.\n\n**Full changelog**: https://github.com/POBSIZ/obsidian-diary/compare/1.7.1...1.8.0",
