      "description": "## What’s new\n\n- Add daily and 3-day 24-hour timeline planners with horizontal scrolling on narrow screens.\n- Add a direct planner view selector and shared year, month, and date navigation.\n- Add independent `start_time` and `end_time` metadata, timed-note creation, and timeline drag interactions.\n- Expand recurrence to every N days, weeks, months, or years with optional end dates and virtual occurrences that create Markdown notes only on demand.\n- Refresh all supported-language documentation, design guidance, and calendar integration notes.\n\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/POBSIZ/obsidian-diary/compare/1.6.0...1.7.0",
